text: Edmund Ironside or Edmund II (; c. 989 – 30 November 1016) was the son of Æthelred the Unready. When his father died he was king of England from 23 April to 18 October 1016 and of Wessex from 23 April to 30 November 1016. Category:989 births Category:1016 deaths Category:House of Wessex
title: Edmund II of England
